      "resolution_criteria": "This question will resolve as **Yes** if, after the question's opening and before September 1, 2026, Instructure or any of its [products](https://www.instructure.com/products) (including but not limited to Canvas, Mastery, Parchment, and Impact) experiences at least one cybersecurity incident that meets any of the following conditions:\n\n1. **Data exfiltration:** An unauthorized party obtains personal data (such as names, email addresses, student IDs, messages, credentials, or financial information) of at least 10,000 users.\n2. **Service disruption:** One or more Instructure products are rendered substantially unavailable to at least 100 institutional customers for a continuous period of at least 4 hours as a direct result of a security breach.\n3. **Ransom or extortion demand:** A threat actor issues a ransom or extortion demand related to data or systems access newly obtained from Instructure.\n\nAll conditions require confirmation from at least one of the following: Instructure official communications, credible news reporting, or government disclosures. An attacker's public claim alone will not be sufficient.",
